trans-unit.source: Defines constants that represent the ways a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView"></xref> can be drawn.
trans-unit.target: Definierar konstanter som representerar hur en <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView"> </xref> kan ritas.

trans-unit.source: This enumeration is used by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeView.DrawMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to indicate whether the nodes or node-labels of a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeView> are owner-drawn.
trans-unit.target: Den här uppräkningen används av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeView.DrawMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskap som anger om noder eller nod-etiketter för en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeView>är ägare ritas.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeView> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeView.DrawMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeView.DrawNode?displayProperty=fullName> event.
The <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView"></xref> is drawn by the operating system.
All elements of a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView"></xref> node are drawn manually, including icons, checkboxes, plus and minus signs, and lines connecting the nodes.
trans-unit.target: Alla element i en <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView"> </xref> node ritas manuellt, inklusive ikoner, kryssrutor, plus och minus tecken och linjer som sammanbinder noderna.

trans-unit.source: The label portion of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView"></xref> nodes are drawn manually.
trans-unit.target: Den etikett som del av den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView"> </xref> noder ritas manuellt.

trans-unit.source: Other node elements are drawn by the operating system, including icons, checkboxes, plus and minus signs, and lines connecting the nodes.
trans-unit.target: Andra nodelement ritas av operativsystemet, inklusive ikoner, kryssrutor, plus och minus tecken och linjer som sammanbinder noderna.
